{"tid":1780731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"No time to die","createTime":"2019-12-12T15:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T03:16:40.000Z","uid":233061,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3bf9fd1defe7896d99363747d09d04119e5e89","tid":1780731,"uid":233061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"英國仲有唔夠一日就會變天，無論工黨定保守黨上台我哋都要繼續迫英國人還BNO條債。<br />\n<br />\n呢一切其實都係歷史錯誤，我哋上一代好多都讀書少，對於回歸都係「是但啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「最緊要有工開」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「改革開放wo」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「50年不變wo」再加上某大黨騎劫兩代港人（而家係三代，好多80，90後都成家立室）話要民主回歸中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到香港今日咁，完全行錯曬路，係時候番番去正軌，向英國表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n對於平權好多人話「人血饅頭」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實呢個絕對係一個謬誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不排除5毛分化）正如國際關係學者沈旭暉教授所講...<br />\n<br />\n「關於遲出生的一代真香港人，根據國際關係案例，先例一開、其他法例齊來，除了可以帶同未成年子女，也可以優先申請成年家人團聚，或和英聯邦身份掛鉤讓各國共同承擔，或改變BNO申請資格，或讓其他BNO持有人排short-cut，方法很多，總之不可能只有廢老獲利。這點，道可道非常道。」<br />\n<br />\n香港情況十分險峻，記住我地已經NO TIME TO DIE！加入BN(O)HK，兄弟爬山，一齊爬BNO平權戰線之山，為香港人提供強大保護盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6KWrUn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6KWrUn.jpg&h=aa0864cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PjfHsL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PjfHsL.jpg&h=ae3bfff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTG：<a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=20ee4460\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"},{"pid":"b228d